'''Kimr''' is an ethnic group in [[West Darfur]] in [[Sudan]] and [[Chad]]. They speak Gimr, a dialect of [[Tama language|Tama]], a Nilo-Saharan language. The population of this ethnicity possibly is below 10,000.
